%h2
  Step 2: Enter Code

%form{method: 'GET', action: '/mobile/token'}
  %fieldset
    = Rack::Csrf.tag(env)
    %label
      Enter your mobile phone in
      %a{href: 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E.164'} E.164
      format:
    %input{type: 'text', name: 'phone', value: phone, readonly: true}
    %label
      Enter the auth code received:
    %input{type: 'text', name: 'code', maxlength: 4, size: 8, pattern: '[0-9]+', autocomplete: 'off', required: true, tabindex: 1, autofocus: true}
    %input{type: 'submit', tabindex: 2, value: 'Login'}

%p
  If you didn't receive the code, go
  %a{href: iri.cut('/mobile_send')} back
  and try again.
  You are allowed to make three attempts per day.
